column5: Have been doing fly-ins to Birch Lake with Peter Kay at KayAir. This year taking my dad, and my 14 year old son on his first great northern adventure. Need some help on fishing spots, advice, etc for Lac Seul out of Peter's cabins in Ear Falls area...thanks in advance.
What time of the year are you going? Where is Peter's cabins?Pooch
Peters cabins sit right at his base...just south of ear falls...close to whitewing? I believe
